com.googlecode.openbeans

Class XMLDecoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.openbeans.XMLDecoder

  • public class XMLDecoder
extends Object
    XMLDecoder reads objects from xml created by XMLEncoder.

    The API is similar to ObjectInputStream.
